                  <summary> The paper manuscript is written in Grantha script with black ink pen.  At the centre title Vivādabhaṅgārṇava In the left side hariḥ oṃ at the centre below the title śrīgurūbhyo namaḥ and in the right corner is written śubhamastu. It is a part of Dāyabhāga a text on Dharmaśāstra .</summary>
                  
